appearance with a huge array of armour and weapon cosmetics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/a7eb29dc14385a0cbe5ac59801ec24cc.avif?t=1774004924\" width=780 height=207 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/0b9935af0cf7792fe78b3dba28cc6ba1.avif?t=1774004924\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/f5ec2b6f71789b7aae7a252f19ac439d.poster.avif?t=1774004924\" width=610 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/f5ec2b6f71789b7aae7a252f19ac439d.webm?t=1774004924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/f5ec2b6f71789b7aae7a252f19ac439d.mp4?t=1774004924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Tear through unending waves of Tyranid and Chaos assaults and fight to survive as long as you can in the unforgiving 3-player Siege mode. Accumulate points with each wave you defeat to spend on ammunition, equipment charges, Medicae Stimms and more… or use them to summon reinforcements like Cadians, Space Marines or the mighty Dreadnought.</p>",
